name: HMCDE CASE n.1
description:
it's 2 am in the morning, when in the end of his night shift, officer dunham got 10-56 from dispatch unit telling that he must go to crime scene immediately in case the person is still alive. Officer dunham is first to come in crime scene, what he found is very disturbing, he found male caucassian around 30 hanging themself in the street light but there is a many little stab wound in his belly, what happened to the victim, and who call the 911 for emergency?when there is not even a single person around the crime scene.

1st artwork from total 5 artwork series. @mohamad_slamet1
